# Messerschmitt Bf-109 G12 Addon
# author: Sebastian (rollershutter)
#
# this is a Addon for the existing bf109 by dfaber, simply copy the content into your existing bf109 folder.

This is the trainer-variant of the popular Messerschmitt Bf 109.
In the real thing, the main fueltank was resized due to the installation of the second cockpit-place so the droptank would be default equippment (This is not yet represented by a new FDM-file).

